title: Thule T2 Pro XT platform bike rack

image.name: Thule T2 Pro XT platform bike rack
image.description:
This rack for 1.25 inch hitches only.
T2 Pro XT is Thule's premium platform hitch bike rack, and possibly the easiest way to carry bikes behind your car. 
Easy to install and remove the rack with the tool-free AutoAttach system. 
Carrier easily folds when not in use and tilts away from vehicle for rear access.
Lock bikes to the rack and secure the rack to the receiver with the integrated cable lock and lock knob.
Ideal for carbon frames, mountain, downhill, and fat bikes as it fits 20 - 29" wheels and up to 5" tires without adapters.
Load capacity: 120 lbs
Max bike weight: 60 lbs
